#CPQA INCLUDE  eau-vide.crd  
#CPQA INCLUDE  eau-vide.inp
#CPQA INCLUDE  eau-vide.top
#CPQA TEST SCALAR 'ChkSum\(DIP\) = ' 2

&INFO
 Vapor/Liquid interface CPMD + GRIMME dispersion 
 QM/MM input file - Add coordinates, topology & input MM
&END

&CPMD
  USE_CUFFT 
  FFT_N_STREAMS_PER_DEVICE
  2
  FFT_N_DEVICES_PER_TASK
  1
  USE_CUBLAS
  BLAS_N_STREAMS_PER_DEVICE
  2
  BLAS_N_DEVICES_PER_TASK
  1
  MOLECULAR DYNAMICS BO 
  INITIALIZE WAVEFUNCTION ATOM
  restart wavefunction coordinates accumulators latest 
  QUENCH ELECTRONS BO
  MIRROR
  ODIIS
  5
  CONVERGENCE ORBITAL
  1.0D-4
  CONVERGENCE GEOMETRY
  1.0D-4
  GDIIS   
  5
  MEMORY BIG small
  DIPOLE DYNAMICS SAMPLE WANNIER
  1 
  WANNIER TYPE resta VANDERBILT
  WANNIER PARAMETER
   0.2  1.E-05  0.01  1000
  wannier reference
   0.0000  0.0000  0.0000
  TRAJECTORY SAMPLE XYZ 
   1
  MAXSTEP
  1 
  TIMESTEP
   4.0 
  EMASS
   380.00
  STORE
  50
  VDW CORRECTION
  QMMM
&END

&DFT
  NEWCODE
  FUNCTIONAL BLYP
  GC-CUTOFF
  0.1E-06
&END
  
&SYSTEM
 POISSON TUCKERMAN
 EXTERNAL FIELD
 0.001 0.000 0.000
 SYMMETRY
  0
 angstrom
 CELL ABSOLUTE
  41.6000  20.0000  20.0000  0.0  0.0  0.0
  original true values of whole box in Angstrom 31.00 15.6404 15.6404
 CUTOFF
  15.0
 CHARGE
  0
&END 

&VDW
 EMPIRICAL CORRECTION
 VDW PARAMETERS
  ALL DFT-D2
 S6GRIMME
  BLYP
 END EMPIRICAL CORRECTION
&END

&QMMM
 COORDINATES
  eau-vide.crd
 TOPOLOGY
  eau-vide.top
 INPUT
  eau-vide.inp
 AMBER gromos
 LONG RANGE ELECTROSTATIC COUPLING
 RCUT_NN
  10.0
 RCUT_MIX
  15.0
 RCUT_ESP
  25.0
 TIMING
 MAXNAT
 3000
 NOSPLIT split
 ARRAYSIZES
 MAXATT 102
 MAXAA2 428
 MAXNRP 484
 MAXNBT 502
 MAXBNH 456
 MAXBON 400
 MAXTTY 400
 MXQHEH 400
 MAXTH  400
 MAXQTY 400
 MAXHIH 400
 MAXQHI 400
 MAXPTY 400
 MXPHIH 400
 MAXPHI 400
 MAXCAG 428
 MAXAEX 20384
 MXEX14 400
 MAXINB 10000
 MAXJNB 1000000
 END ARRAYSIZES

&END

